Shen has low attack range and damage scaling which, combined with the fact that taunt will usually place him deep in the enemy team, means that Shen works best when he's durable.  

If you want to build damage on Shen, I would recommend picking up one or two of the damage items which scale independent of your abilities.  Some good options:
